flowchart LR
  Operator[Operador humano] --> Canvas[Canvas Live]
  Canvas --> Gateway[Gateway API]
  Gateway --> Bedrock[AWS Bedrock Claude]
  Bedrock --> Tools[Tool calling OpenClaw]
  Tools --> ReadScratch[read_episodic_scratch]
  Tools --> CompactIntent[compact_intent]
  Tools --> Orchestrator[configure_complete_smtp]
  Orchestrator --> ApprovalGate[ApprovalGate 1 firma]
  ApprovalGate --> Providers[Route53 / Webdock / IONOS / SMTP]
  Providers --> Audit[Audit chain SHA-256]
  Orchestrator --> CompactIntent
  CompactIntent --> Scratch[(Postgres openclaw_episodic_scratch)]
  ReadScratch --> Scratch
  Scratch --> Bedrock
  Scratch --> TtlJob[TTL job env-gated]
  TtlJob --> Audit
  Gateway --> Logs[Canvas Terminal logs]
  Audit --> Canvas
